Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(248,261)\fs20\fad(650,900)}熱風!狂飆!碓冰山道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常不妙 我能行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方能行的話 我沒可能不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著 緊貼內線 抓地過彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得好 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,障礙物 讓出內線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有兩下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是普通的車手呢 緊咬著不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都做不到 到後面就沒有樂趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟到什麼程度呢 我們的實力可不僅止於此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真夠嗆 無法自己駕馭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能被動跟跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就像過山車一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法作出自己的節奏 所以才覺得可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這裏被甩開的話就絕對追不上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不熟悉道路 比想像中更加不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意力減退的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是撞上山壁就是摔落谷底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是如今轟動一時的秋名86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那麼容易甩開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為是右轉 其實是左轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是碓冰彎道的恐怖之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著右轉 很窄哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎麼能被你甩開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方能轉的話 我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.32,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子 他說對方能轉自己應該也能轉是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很肯定地說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信 非常單純的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的腦子裏到底裝了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但換句話說那是個了不起的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有他那樣的技術是想不出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說入彎不超出極限還是能控制的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說當然能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.12,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可對手怎麼說也是對道路瞭如指掌...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然會將速度提至極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海也用同樣的速度入彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這一無所知的碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不寒而慄啊 光是想就覺得恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是技術 沒有過人的膽識也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.93,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍有閃失車就會完全報廢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像說對手是什麼Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80是什麼車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被咬住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼? 是我開得不好嗎? 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有的事 你狀態很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可他緊跟在後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別看後視鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會影響節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面的動向我會好好留心 沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是才開始嘛 要好好享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是最棒的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 交給我吧 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是 請相信搭檔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子和我是碓冰最快的最佳組合哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行者將後追者甩開就算贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法甩開的話再互換位置 直到決出勝負為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是驟死賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種規則的話 第一輪肯定選先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為能確保拖延到第二輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有一輪可以練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二輪輸了也沒那麼難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一輪我從後面出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再想清楚 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的比賽 我自己會決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我是不喜歡後面被人跟著才選的後追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到會這麼危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生疏的道路上跑 最難的一點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是決定入彎速度的判斷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟介輸掉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及中裏的32被超都是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.37,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管技術再好也贏不了長期在本地跑的車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼要贏秋名86的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能贏 憑這個理論的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在他的主場秋名山也能贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 太小看她們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下了個危險之極的賭注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入彎前僅有幾厘米的路線誤差...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或速度誤差的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出彎後就會發展成巨大的誤差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保險杠擦到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 絕不能被甩開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多體驗幾次心臟極度收縮的瞬間 車手才會成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與眾不同的注意力和感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千錘百煉的駕駛技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上最重要的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我親手炮製完美的懸掛設定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會輸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣了呢? 已經有結果了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒回來前還不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.91,0:11:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太勉強了 再怎麼偏袒也找不到有利條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 池谷前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.26,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前也沒有一個條件對拓海有利過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中裏的32那像怪物般的車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊司那傢伙的膠帶死亡賽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對拓海來說都是初次經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此拓海仍有唯一的優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是地點在秋名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海五年間每天都不斷在跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.15,0:12:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 道路不同 真會有那麼大的影響?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑幾次的話情況還好點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可拓海完完全全是第一次跑這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 池谷 我有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.04,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子助手席上的那個女孩是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問我 我還想問你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是比賽 還理所當然地坐在旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳情我也不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只聽說好像是童年的至交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.53,0:12:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初學時兩人總是一起研究...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並完成了駕駛技術的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.79,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就像是拉力賽的領航員一樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來拓海就更不利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 拓海沒理由輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果身旁有優秀的領航員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子只需注意駕駛就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎道前有障礙物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲開後再佔回內線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甩不掉 這樣的高節奏仍然跟得上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子在絕佳狀態居然還被咬住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.75,0:14:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子 馬上就到C=121了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入口開始就盡全力滑過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強行一次性解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這碓冰山道最難的彎道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白 就這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他見識一下從入口一直甩到出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒人用和我同樣速度入彎後能成功出彎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子和沙雪今晚不來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.09,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道呢 還沒見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想看Sil-80的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這C=121彎道是最棒的觀察點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難度也極高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不能用難來形容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在這兒從入口一直甩到出口的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就稱得上是碓冰山道的高手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰的高手 到哪兒都是最強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒膽量一口氣拚死入彎的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.49,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度不夠 漂移就無法持續到出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次嘗試的人全都失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但熟練之後也有人能做到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.65,0:16:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能以全油門不剎車入彎就只有真子的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道她大概練了多久才掌握的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那種程度卻沒人能模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人從上面下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好響的輪胎尖叫聲 要衝過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.96,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真子和沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面還有車 是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在比賽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是86嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有對向車 華麗地沖吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入彎了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以理解 居然以真子同樣的速度入彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知死活的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不知道C=121的難度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不是靠什麼狗屎膽量就能成功的彎道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有毅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然能緊貼著真子入彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.29,0:17:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了這種速度就只能憑真本事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.83,0:17:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C=121中間很寬敞 但出口卻極端狹窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去路線很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能成功的卻只有一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.73,0:18:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第一次跑的道路上 第一輪就能駕馭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那86是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...難道那傢伙就是最近盛傳的秋名86?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雞皮疙瘩都起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超極限速度的四輪漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是Ultra D的難度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連熟練了的真子出彎時與最佳路線也差了五厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那傢伙卻修正至理想線路出了彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,選了個相差懸殊的怪物來做比賽對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯了 這彎道動作不能那麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請在入彎前說啊 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 別發呆啊 不像平時的你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不明白 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面的86是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是現在的我們能應付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 平時不是很愛逞強嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.26,0:20:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還沒輸你就想放棄了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是沒錯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 沒想到你那麼膽怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能再靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那輛86的厲害不是早就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.91,0:20:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但已經決定這是最後的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們不全力以赴的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就都結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道你在害怕什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的沙雪最差勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是助手席上的累贅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累贅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是個會破壞功重比的壓艙物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.47,0:20:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一握方向盤人就變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說我是壓艙物算什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是身材好 我又不是肥婆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可還是多了四十九公斤的不利因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是四十七公斤!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到這份上也不能再忍氣吞聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拚命地沖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.36,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 下個彎道 用幾乎撞上內側岩石的氣勢切入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不顧後果地追跑到現在已經完全習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我掌握了這條山道的節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能以自己的節奏來跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的彎道不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不到最後不能洩氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.31,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝刺 衝刺 再衝刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.34,0:22:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想留下悔恨 即使賭上碓冰山道最快的尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.50,0:24:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文太先生 和Sil-80的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.45,0:24:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海有勝算嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.40,0:24:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.42,0:24:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.34,0:24:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是開豆腐店的 不是預言家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.55,0:24:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我煎豆腐餅和炸豆腐塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.90,0:24:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是我精心炮製的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.08,0:24:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下山的話絕不會輸給任何車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.67,0:24:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然還要根據車手的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.46,0:24:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬請期待下星期吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.80,0:24:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.75,0:24:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木棉豆腐和絹豆腐我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.11,0:24:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 頭文字D 決戰!超級漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.16,0:24:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.44,0:24:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別錯過

